title: Follow 2015 District 11 girls tennis doubles tournaments (BRACKETS)
text:
Liberty's Samantha Peterson, pictured, and Madelyn Conrad are the top seed in the District 11 Class AAA doubles tournament. (lehighvalleylive.com file photo) By Josh Folck | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 16, 2015 1:39 AM, updated October 16, 2015 2:41 AM View/Post Comments 
The District 11 Class AA and AAA doubles tournaments continue on Friday. 
Saucon Valley High School will host Friday's quarterfinals and semifinals in both classes. The seeded teams advanced to the quarterfinals in both AA and AAA. 
The finals will be held Monday at Lehigh University.
